<div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
  <h1>Your ingredients:</h1>
  <ul class="list-unstyled">
    <li>1 cup <%= @flour %></li>
    <li>1/2 teaspoon baking powder</li>
    <li>1/3 - 1/2 cup <%= @sugar %></li>
    <li>5 table spoons <%= @fat %></li>
    <li>1/2 - 3/4 cup <%= @liquid %></li>
    <li>1/2 cup <%= @optional %></li>
    <% @spices.each do |spice| -%>
    <li><%= spice %></li>
    <% end -%>
  </ul><h1>Your recipe:</h1>
  <p>Whisk all dry ingredients together in a bowl. Make a well in the middle and add <%= @fat %>, <%= @liquid %>,
    and the <%= @optional %>. Mix. Transfer to a 20x20 cm baking pan or muffin forms.
  </p>
  <p>
    Bake in around 200 degrees Celsius for 20-30 minutes. Just stare at the oven. Use a chopstick or toothpick
    to see if the cake is done.
  </p>
